{
  "stem": "26111.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In London, I was-- I got a job, as I think I mentioned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was, very shortly after that, called up for war work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I should add that I made efforts during the entire-- these entire years to get into the armed forces.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my nationality, which was still German-- even though I was classified as a refugee from Nazi oppression, a bona fide refugee-- and why I was not treated-- i.e. in turn, I was not treated like, like real Germans-- Nazi-type Germans.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And nonetheless, I was not accepted into the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I made efforts to get into the US Army as soon as-- as soon as the-- as soon as the US entered the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in fact, I now remember-- I hadn't told this before-- is that I even made-- when Mexico-- I read somewhere that Mexico entered the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I wrote to the Mexican embassy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I got a letter back in Spanish, and I-- which, which I knew by that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had taken Spanish classes at one of my-- one of my-- one of my years in Bradford.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and the, the answer was a very polite no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In fact, I don't think any, any Mexican forces were engaged in the-- in the-- in the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it was a declaration.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a political thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyway, I couldn't get in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in-between, I managed to-- I had-- I should add that I had managed to matriculate from school, get-- in other words, high school matriculation in England was the same thing as a high school certificate and university entry examen combined.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had passed that before leaving Bradford.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had come back from the evacuated school because they, they, they were hopeless.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't teach me anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
